    <p>{`Try to change your default. Switch to other browser. Kill all notifications, or remove all apps from your phone. You don’t need to quit social apps forever, but play this game and maybe you’ll get something valuable about yourself. Or you’ll find a better way to use apps, your own non default way!`}</p>

